data.oai_dc:dc: Tanana River Yearly Ice Break Up Observed at Nenana, AK (1917 - Present)

This is a Yearly observation of when the ice on the Tanana River breaks up. This data is hosted originally by the National snow and ice data enter(http://nsidc.org/). The data is located at http://nsidc.org/data/docs/daac/nsidc0064_nenana.gd.html .
